      actions: { en: `Address leadership alignment as the absolute top priority. Honestly assess whether the current leadership team can execute this strategy. Consider external leadership support, interim capability, or recruitment for critical gaps.`, fr: `Address leadership alignment as the absolute top priority. Honestly assess whether the current leadership team can execute this strategy. Consider external leadership support, interim capability, or recruitment for critical gaps.` },
