      actions: { en: `Invest immediately in multi-level strategy translation. Address information flow barriers by creating safe, reliable channels for upward and lateral communication.`, fr: `Invest immediately in multi-level strategy translation. Address information flow barriers by creating safe, reliable channels for upward and lateral communication.` },
